{"tid":985752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"5男女疑「眼超超」惹禍 兩人死跟再被打","createTime":"2019-01-18T01:32:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T14:37:43.000Z","uid":5919,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"78ecf98596b7d71e4e054ea572fb31caa8a20719","tid":985752,"uid":5919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T01:32:19.000Z","msg":"旺角豉油街90號地下7-11便利店，昨晚11時許，3男2女購物時疑因目光問題，與9男1女爭執，該批男女部份身有酒氣，向5人襲擊，3男更被按地毆打，同行兩女亦捱打同告受傷。兇徒之後分別乘的士及徒步離去。<br />\n<br />\n其中遇襲的姓鍾25歲男子及姓江26歲女子心有不甘，尾隨步行一方約300米至窩打老道與太平道交界火車橋附近，被發現後又被毆打，兇徒其後逃去。<br />\n<br />\n警方接報到場，將鍾男及江女，以及姓鄧21歲女子、姓謝25歲及姓葉25歲男子送院。警方調查案件，追緝涉事兇徒下落。<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190118&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59155511\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190118%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59155511&d=e09FmYdHwEhMRyOr1dZ1njQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=c8af6952\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190118%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59155511&h=6b013ae3\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190118&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59155511</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5072a73de2e18f2eb59cccd2d01e37f23ae5935d","tid":985752,"uid":32615,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T01:33:44.000Z","msg":"5p<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19ecb3409a7a95fc70d2f6f941b03c7f55f8a3b8","tid":985752,"uid":72735,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T01:38:45.000Z","msg":"比人打多獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要醉貓都打唔贏"},{"pid":"573f57c12bb2789a98ac1333742e542e802ec7c9","tid":985752,"uid":1247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T01:40:42.000Z"